rows.label: qst202912_0030
rows.name:
Are you all right?
You're not hurt, are you, hon?

rows.label: qst202912_0050
rows.name:
Well, that is a relief.
I was real worried, you know.

rows.label: qst202912_0070
rows.name:
Monsters?!
Ugh, where'd this lot pop up from?!

rows.label: qst202912_0080
rows.name:
I fear we may have wandered
into their territory.

rows.label: qst202912_0120
rows.name:
Don't you worry, hon.
You'll be just fine with us, I promise.

rows.label: qst202912_0130
rows.name:
I'm not just a pretty lady, you know...
I can also kick monster heinie!

rows.label: qst202912_0140
rows.name:
So you just sit tight while we take
care o' these critters!
